properties.areaDesc: Eastern Norton Sound and Nulato Hills
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 5 at 3:52PM AKST until February 6 at 12:00AM AKST by NWS Fairbanks, AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow and blowing snow occurring. Plan on difficult travel
conditions. Additional snow accumulation of 1 inch expected.
Blowing snow will reduce visibility to one half mile or less at
times.

* WHERE...Eastern Norton Sound and Nulato Hills near St Michael.

* WHEN...Until midnight.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Conditions are much less severe north of St
Michael.
properties.instruction:
A Winter Weather Advisory for snow means periods of snow will
cause travel difficulties.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL MIDNIGHT AKST TONIGHT
